"Wireless_IPSetting_Help_Body":"<h4>Introduction</h4><p>Type in the Private LAN IP Address. The Private LAN IP Address is the gateway's IP address as seen by users on the network.</p><p>Type in the Subnet Mask. Subnet Mask allows for the definition of the subnet size.</p><p>Type in the DHCP Start IP. This will be the first available IP Address that will be assigned by the DHCP.</p><p>Type in the DHCP End IP. This will be the last available IP Address that will be assigned by the DHCP.</p><br/><h4>Button</h4><p>This <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" title=\"Apply Button\" data-content=\"And here's some amazing content. It's very engaging. right?\">Save changes</a> should save the data and submit the form.</p><p>This <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"btn\" title=\"Cancel Button\" data-content=\"And here's some amazing content. It's very engaging. right?\">Cancel</a> should reset the all data.</p><p>This <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"btn\" title=\"Help Button\" data-content=\"And here's some amazing content. It's very engaging. right?\">Help</a> should show the configure guide.</p><br/>",

